data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!!!!This Stunning home in the beautiful Cascata Falls Addition is awaiting a new owner!!! This home features four large bedrooms and a very spacious bonus room that could actually be a fifth bedroom if needed. All four bedrooms are on the main floor each with private ensuite bathroom. Primary bedroom is very spacious with large walk-in closet and spa like bathroom. Beautiful living area with tranquil fireplace with a remote start and lovely Levolor blinds with remote or Levolor app for anytime. HVAC downstairs replaced in Sept. 2023, water heater 2022, and a plug for a portable generator was installed in the garage. Flooring is beautiful thru out the home with wood floors, gorgeous tile and new carpet in 2 eastside bedrooms. Awesome community with lots of activities and the sought after award winning Edmond school system. This home has so much to offer you don't want to miss it. BOOK YOUR PRIVATE SHOWING TODAY!!!
